SharpClaw: They sometimes surprise me. As foolish as they are they sometimes prove to be warriors.
SharpClaw went back to working on her wounds. He ignored the alarms to help her.
 raccoon7679 <raccoon7679@...> wrote:KitKat::

She looked at him, then reset the sword in the holder on her thigh. 
She wobbled while sitting on the table. "I am fine. I am just low on 
energon."  She looks at her body, "And some holes patched up. By the 
Pit, I had no idea those slagging Maximals could shoot."
